LOADING DATA

library(readxl)
gemaps <- read.csv("C:/Users/Joyce/Downloads/Stats141XP_FinalProject/Fw_ Data for Voice_Personality study/round1_gemaps.csv")
accoustic <- read_excel("C:/Users/Joyce/Downloads/Stats141XP_FinalProject/BigC_BIGC_ACOUSTIC_ANALYSES.xlsx")
assesment <- read.csv("C:/Users/Joyce/Downloads/Stats141XP_FinalProject/BigCAssessments.csv")
library(ggplot2)

CLEANING DATA

# Removing "work" PTID
gemaps1 <- subset(gemaps, !subject_id == "work")

# Joining Datasets
merged_df <- merge(assesment, gemaps1, by.x = "PTID", by.y = "subject_id")

# Selecting Columns
library(dplyr)
## 
## Attaching package: 'dplyr'
## The following objects are masked from 'package:stats':
## 
##     filter, lag
## The following objects are masked from 'package:base':
## 
##     intersect, setdiff, setequal, union
clean <- dplyr::select(merged_df, PTID, file_length.seconds., F0semitoneFrom27.5Hz_sma3nz_amean, F0semitoneFrom27.5Hz_sma3nz_stddevNorm, group, sex, age, jitterLocal_sma3nz_amean,jitterLocal_sma3nz_stddevNorm, shimmerLocaldB_sma3nz_amean, shimmerLocaldB_sma3nz_stddevNorm)

colnames(clean) <- c("PTID", "duration", "tone_mean", "tone_sd", "group", "sex", "age", "jitter_mean", "jitter_sd", "shimmer_mean", "shimmer_sd")

# Converting to Factor
variables_to_convert <- c("group", "sex")
clean[variables_to_convert] <- lapply(clean[variables_to_convert], factor)
clean$PTID <- as.character(clean$PTID)

# Reduced Accoustic for Variables of Interest
accoustic_red <- select(accoustic, PTID, ANXIETY, DEPRESSION, DUTIFULNESS, MODESTY, ORDERLINESS, ACTIVITY_LEVEL,
                        IMAGINATION, LIBERALISM, ACHIEVEMENT_STRIVING, IMMODERATION, EXCITEMENT_SEEKING, EMOTIONALITY) 

full <- merge(clean, accoustic_red, by.x = "PTID", by.y = "PTID")

full$creative <- ifelse(full$group == "Ctrl", "No", "Yes")

#write.csv(full, "full_voice_data.csv")

ggplot(full, aes(x = group, y = tone_mean, fill = group)) + 
  geom_violin(trim = FALSE) +
  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#cceafaff", "#1da677ff", "#e096beff")) +
  geom_boxplot(color="black", fill="white", width=0.1) +
  ggtitle("Violin Plot of Tone Mean for Each Group") +
  xlab("Group") + ylab("Tone Mean")
